# Dependencies
node_modules/
# Lock files MUST be committed for reproducible CI builds (npm ci requires them).
# Previously gitignored due to platform-specific binary pollution; that issue is
# solved by always running npm install on a clean node_modules, not by excluding
# the lock file. See DEVELOPER_GUIDE.md and lessons.md L-033.

